			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=31262&amp;sid=18f225b7519c2ade13341862f3ae88f6#p31262"><img src="./styles/Carbon/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>			by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=29342&amp;sid=18f225b7519c2ade13341862f3ae88f6">The Riviera Kid</a></strong> on Fri Dec 11, 2009 2:47 pm			<br />([msg=31262]see Re: My First Game --- C++[/msg])
